    <j.0:event_legal_comment xml:lang="en">Most of the amendments which can be accepted by the Commission contain useful technical clarifications or additions to the proposed definitions of the Commission's proposal.  The majority of the amendments to be rejected by the Commission relate to the substance ban and the calculation of the collection target for all portable batteries. </j.0:event_legal_comment>
